name: Platform #1
description:

< ENG translation > 

Put your headphone
loose yourself, dream.

When you realize you're in a maze
That's because you've been there for a while
So do not rush,
Maybe you can learn something in the way.

Maybe you can find something of value,
Maybe you can learn something of value about yourself,
Maybe,

You might wake up a feeling
Maybe your brain can use this time to simulate a few different situations,
Throw away what's not important
Get ready for the future.

In this Labyrinth you'll find characters and places,
Sound and Image,
Time and thought,
Metaphysics and bullshit.

I'll tell you my dreams,
Then you tell me yours.

This is an ornment,
A necklace we make the time wear,
To see if it gets quiet.
